50|$|<b>Hold</b> Your <b>Fire</b> is {{the twelfth}} studio album by Canadian rock band Rush, {{released}} on September 8, 1987. It was recorded at The Manor Studio in Oxfordshire, Ridge Farm Studio in Surrey, Air Studios in Montserrat and McClear Place in Toronto. <b>Hold</b> Your <b>Fire</b> {{was the last}} Rush studio album released outside Canada by PolyGram/Mercury.|$|R
